N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4622.21 - Cashing of checks prohibited

State Regulations

No licensee, its members or agents, shall cash any check
out of games of chance funds or extend credit to a person to participate in the
playing of any games of chance. Notes
